PrecisAssignment to the Minister of the Environment of the administration over certain public lands which are required for wildlife research, conservation or interpretation, including the establishment of two new NATIONAL WILDLIFE AREAS, Portobello Creek in New Brunswick and Nirjutiqavvik in the Northwest Territories, and the expansion of four existing ones, Pointe de l'Est, Lac Saint-François, Cap Tourmente and Pointe-au-Père in Quebec.

Assignment to the Minister of the Environment of the administration over
certain public lands which are required for wildlife research, conservation

Saint-François, Cap Tourmente and Pointe-au-Père in Quebec.
